{"tid":1932002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消除旅遊欲望！台灣最美漫畫店「封書抗疫」！！","createTime":"2020-03-18T12:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T13:43:05.000Z","uid":209657,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e1d618632566a779c23ea4fd4e37123064982c","tid":1932002,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/18/99/7613539.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=800$&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F18%2F99%2F7613539.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D800%24%26nt%3D1&h=a82e255d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"644cf35658b802066407a9358226f3c7af1b7c29","tid":1932002,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情日益嚴峻，台灣近日確診病例也從本土案例轉變為境外移入案例，出國旅遊被視為防疫破口，對近幾例因旅遊染病者更是罵聲不絕。高雄一間租書店為從根源杜絕出國欲望，鐵腕「封書」禁止顧客翻閱。<br />\n<br />\n近日因新北市里長在全台防疫期間揪團赴歐洲旅遊，引發外界批評和醫護人員反彈，網路上也針對此時出國究竟是「不得已」還是「自私」加以討論。高雄一間號稱「全台最美漫畫店」鑑於台灣境外確診病例連日飆高，昨晚（17日）於臉書粉專宣布，為防止大家受到漂亮照片影響，腦波一弱就皮癢的訂下特價機票，即刻起至疫情結束前，店內所有境外旅遊書籍皆不得翻閱！"},{"pid":"6327209357dd396e52d15faee657dd6c28880ed2","tid":1932002,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/18/99/7613540.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930$&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F18%2F99%2F7613540.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%24%26nt%3D1&h=260e8aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店家說到做到地將相關書籍貼滿封條，要求顧客勿伸手觸碰，「違者將獲得永世大便都沒衛生紙的詛咒」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而為了滿足無法冷靜待在室內，就是想往外跑的顧客，店家也提供國內旅遊相關書籍，讓大家一解旅遊欲望，強調「放心玩才好玩」。"},{"pid":"b18a16a01bff813ee2277ed56642784e5b706f4c","tid":1932002,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"書店FB：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bookingbookstore/posts/3265510086811553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbookingbookstore%2Fposts%2F3265510086811553&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=81bab044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bookingbookstore/posts/3265510086811553</a><br />\nSauce:<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120913/4424181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120913%2F4424181&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=c7d73465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120913/4424181</a>"},{"pid":"e3ad12d7bec141f2238fd13a05526ad5b6f4ce9f","tid":1932002,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae02dc6f4681c718fd52ea4282224190761e4a85","tid":1932002,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"返校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a041d0a7d95537973b145f6d271c9d07accbf94","tid":1932002,"uid":4811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"其實香港圖書館開返感覺勁撚污糟"},{"pid":"cf6ccc87198cfd2ffd38e5976149d6155dcf30e5","tid":1932002,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"唔係更應該開放卑大家睇<br />\n睇完當去左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5578e5fce0f41919eeea7f9e1a64d